00:49.484 --> 00:55.612
And it's a classic example of how to receive our healing from God by faith.

00:56.573 --> 00:57.394
This woman,

00:58.082 --> 01:09.920
had a sickness that no doctor could cure, but she came to Jesus and received, was restored to full health by receiving his healing power.

01:10.540 --> 01:11.101
Praise God.

01:11.141 --> 01:18.652
