02:30.408 --> 02:35.215
And so faith came to our heart because she heard about Jesus.

02:35.255 --> 02:49.496
And this thing we call faith or trust, which is in our heart, is what connects us to God and His grace and His healing power.

02:50.137 --> 02:53.842
