And when she touched him by faith, that power flowed.

24:24.984 --> 24:28.449
And then finally, her fourth action was she told it.

24:29.170 --> 24:38.023
She told her testimony because when he wanted to know who this woman was, it says in verse 33, she told him the whole truth.

24:38.504 --> 24:39.946
She told her testimony.

24:40.327 --> 24:42.149
She told everything about what she did.

24:42.190 --> 24:44.974
And that's how this got recorded in the Bible.

24:45.294 --> 24:49.300
For our example, for our instruction, praise God.

24:49.641 --> 24:50.642
And so when we

24:50.818 --> 24:51.879
receive our healing.

24:52.320 --> 24:54.843
We should start telling it.

24:55.424 --> 24:56.786
We should share our testimony.

24:57.086 --> 25:00.571
But also, it's good to keep declaring.

25:01.632 --> 25:07.199
If you've truly come to Jesus and received His healing power, then a process begins of healing.

25:07.640 --> 25:12.146
And you need to keep declaring that Jesus is healing me.

25:12.446 --> 25:15.109
His healing power is working in my body.

25:15.570 --> 25:18.674
You don't have to kind of pretend that you're healed

25:18.850 --> 25:20.693
when that healing isn't manifested.

25:20.733 --> 25:26.843
But what you can do is you believe you receive healing power spiritually in your heart.

25:27.103 --> 25:31.270
It's with your heart that you believe you receive the blessing of God.

25:31.330 --> 25:33.513
It's in spiritual form.

25:33.914 --> 25:39.022
You can believe you receive it even before you see anything because it's something that's spiritual.

25:40.004 --> 25:42.508
Don't think in terms of a physical manifestation.

25:42.868 --> 25:46.514
Just believe you receive spiritually and then

25:46.658 --> 25:56.549
keep thanking him that that healing power is working in your body to bring about a healing and a cure to restore your health and just keep thanking him.

25:57.811 --> 26:00.614
Declare that his healing power is working.

26:01.134 --> 26:10.285
All right and so this is an example for us of hell to receive healing.

26:10.365 --> 26:14.930
Notice in Mark 6 even the next chapter that

26:15.426 --> 26:18.851
other people were inspired by what happened with her.

26:18.871 --> 26:21.716
And they did the same thing and with the same results.

26:22.296 --> 26:36.718
It says in Mark 6, 55 to 56, whenever he entered into villages, cities or the country, they laid the sick in the marketplaces and begged him that they might just touch the hem of his garment.

26:36.738 --> 26:38.681
And as many as touched him were made well.

26:39.242 --> 26:41.906
So in other words, it wasn't just a special thing for her.

26:42.210 --> 26:46.395
People realized that the healing power of Jesus was available for anyone.

26:46.975 --> 26:55.325
So through this woman's testimony and through her faith, many, many multitudes of people were healed everywhere because this story got round.

26:55.445 --> 26:57.327
But I think she was the pioneer.

26:57.788 --> 27:01.532
She was the one who took Jesus, it is worth that healing power is available.

27:02.072 --> 27:07.378
And you know, it's still true today because that was true in the ministry of Jesus.

27:08.179 --> 27:10.642
But through his death and resurrection,

27:11.298 --> 27:17.647
He has poured out His Holy Spirit and His Holy Spirit is now available for us today.

27:18.488 --> 27:23.454
And part of the power that we receive is healing power.

27:24.015 --> 27:30.263
There's healing power in the Holy Spirit because Jesus on the cross, He purchased our healing.

27:32.406 --> 27:33.728
People often make the mistake.

27:33.768 --> 27:38.194
They try to receive a manifestation and then they pray and then

27:38.530 --> 27:42.536
They look to their body and there's no manifestation and then they say, oh, it didn't work.

27:43.036 --> 27:48.284
But what you're actually, there's no biblical basis to receive an instant manifestation from God.

27:48.865 --> 27:57.397
What there is a biblical basis for is that Jesus heals us by His healing power through the Holy Spirit.

27:57.998 --> 28:04.968
And we have the right to, as children of God, because healing is the children's bread.

28:05.509 --> 28:06.450
In other words,

28:06.754 --> 28:18.808
we can pray, give us today our daily bread, healing belongs to us through our covenant with the Lord, and therefore we can come and we must receive our healing in the form of healing power.

28:19.909 --> 28:27.738
And as we do that, His healing power will flow, praise God, and restore us over a period of time.

28:27.799 --> 28:29.020
How quickly it happens?

28:29.440 --> 28:34.226
We don't know, it all, it depends on the problem, it depends on our faith.

28:34.402 --> 28:38.128
as it were as to how much that healing power can flow.

28:38.148 --> 28:44.678
But if we will just continue to keep the switch of faith turned on, that healing power will work.

28:44.698 --> 28:45.500
So let's just pray.

28:45.580 --> 28:49.386
Father God, I come to you now in the name of Jesus.

28:49.807 --> 28:50.988
I thank you that you love me.

28:51.008 --> 28:59.081
You want me to be healed and that you freely and generously give healing power to all who ask you through your death on the cross.

29:00.263 --> 29:02.066
Jesus, you've purchased my healing.

29:02.306 --> 29:10.138
So right now, according to your word, I believe I receive your healing power to start flowing into my body right now.

29:10.639 --> 29:18.651
And just keep thanking him that his healing power is working, making you whole and saving you from your sickness.

29:18.932 --> 29:22.898
In Jesus name, amen.

